### Health and Service Status
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Prometheus Performance Metrics
GET http://localhost:5000/metrics

### User Registration
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "first_name": "Test",
  "last_name": "User",
  "dob": "1990-01-01",
  "mobile_number": "1234567890"
}

### Login (Supports both JSON body and HTTP Basic Auth)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Secure Endpoint Test (Requires JWT from Login)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/secure-ping
Authorization: Basic test@example.com:password123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": "Hello World"
}

### Standard Single UI Calculation (Requires JWT)
# Available product_id values:
# 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 → Standard Term Life
# 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111 → Endowment Plan Classic
# 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222 → Money Back Plan (20yr)
# 33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333 → ULIP Growth Fund
POST http://localhost:5000/api/calculations/calculate
Authorization: Basic test@example.com:password123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "age": 30,
  "policy_term": 20,
  "premium_payment_term": 15,
  "premium_amount": 50000
}

### Scalable Bulk Calculation Mechanism (Requires JWT)
# Uploads multiple policies for async background processing
# premium_amount is in INR (₹)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/bulk/upload
Authorization: Basic test@example.com:password123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "calculations": [
    {
      "product_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "age": 40,
      "policy_term": 15,
      "premium_payment_term": 10,
      "premium_amount": 100000
    },
    {
      "product_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "age": 25,
      "policy_term": 30,
      "premium_payment_term": 30,
      "premium_amount": 25000
    }
  ]
}

### Retrieve Current User Profile (Requires JWT or Basic Auth)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Basic test@example.com:password123

### Logout User Session
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/logout

### Retrieve Bulk Upload Batch Results (Requires JWT or Basic Auth)
# Note: Replace {batch_id} with the actual UUID returned from the /upload endpoint above
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bulk/019d0647-c717-7925-984b-8a9c2d9528c3/results
Authorization: Basic test@example.com:password123
